{"tid":2493794,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"菲臘親王以皇家海軍中尉身份，乘HMS Whelp艦接受日本投降，重光香港","createTime":"2021-04-18T07:32:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T11:05:02.000Z","uid":79563,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"051aad0ade6da76333c839739d44b9511245d104","tid":2493794,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T07:32:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.hkgolden.media/comment/vg3xotrv.luowqxt333t.1rxefu1clhc.2ht.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.hkgolden.media%2Fcomment%2Fvg3xotrv.luowqxt333t.1rxefu1clhc.2ht.jpg&h=f8993977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【菲臘親王逝世】多次來港訪問，曾協助香港重光<br />\n<br />\n英國白金漢宮宣布，王夫菲臘親王逝世，享年99歲。英國王夫菲臘親王出生於1921年，是希臘及丹麥王子，他的祖父便是跟隨俄國沙皇尼古拉二世來港的希臘國王喬治一世。<br />\n<br />\n菲臘親王在二次大戰曾在皇家海軍服役，先後在地中海及法國南部作戰。在大戰最後階段，他在鄒龍號（HMS Whelp）參與沖繩戰役和日本投降。<br />\n<br />\n之後他便隨鄒龍號來到香港，協助香港重光。據親王回憶，在日本駛住香港途中是他最高興旅程之一，因為他們不用再關燈，也可以打開舷窗，甚至可以沖涼。<br />\n<br />\n在1959年，菲臘親王代表皇室訪問香港。他亦感慨香港戰後發展迅速，與他14年前來時已大大不同。"},{"pid":"c361ea810ccd2bbf206baffca89388eb4b937d5c","tid":2493794,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T09:36:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"313eeb5a68a6a46709d281c0d8ee22f47151e0b1","tid":2493794,"uid":282490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T09:38:15.000Z","msg":"God save the queen <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bbfaa717fcbb8738d8fa8394b95089e28f3bfbc","tid":2493794,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T09:39:02.000Z","msg":"佢係好人嚟"},{"pid":"7ebf351816a83e91f7c4ae26afd49324d6ec4234","tid":2493794,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bbfaa717fcbb8738d8fa8394b95089e28f3bfbc","tid":2493794,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T09:39:02.000Z","msg":"佢係好人嚟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T09:40:25.000Z","msg":"但佢長命 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3864fc09a3d187d6e2ecf02e50e3f515e6d0a90","tid":2493794,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T09:49:00.000Z","msg":"甚至可以沖涼？<br />\n點解唔可以沖涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52afdb2fdd998af8b594308628dc6dae3cecfb81","tid":2493794,"uid":6548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3864fc09a3d187d6e2ecf02e50e3f515e6d0a90","tid":2493794,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T09:49:00.000Z","msg":"甚至可以沖涼？<br />\n點解唔可以沖涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T09:50:57.000Z","msg":"果時可能打緊仗唔想晒水 咁打完咪隨便用"},{"pid":"d5d4182d4e621a06d04dc8efe15c598b41b931f3","tid":2493794,"uid":355289,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b3864fc09a3d187d6e2ecf02e50e3f515e6d0a90","tid":2493794,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T09:49:00.000Z","msg":"甚至可以沖涼？<br />\n點解唔可以沖涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T09:52:14.000Z","msg":"戰時排出嘅廚餘同廢物有機會比潛艇track到"},{"pid":"38c992603c3594328178964485b243e4ede4555a","tid":2493794,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T09:54:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b540f674052877f5b9e76e22fec535e1f5fc651a","tid":2493794,"uid":161684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T11:04:12.000Z","msg":"光復第一人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c016c0cac93f7154d9107312680fab68a53f4267","tid":2493794,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T11:05:02.000Z","msg":"感人香港史<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}